profile.title: Artificial Intelligence Art
profile.description:
The first ever AI Art NFT series. AI Art House is the premier marketplace for AI-generated art, now releasing a limited collection of 1000 works as one-of-a-kind collectible NFTs. Each artwork is a 1/1 piece of AI history, meaning you will own a 100% unique collectors item that nobody else in the world will ever have. As AI Art continues to advance into the future, you will forever own one of its earliest creations.

In 2021, AI Art House has already been featured in T3, Uncrate, The Peak, and more.
